.fi
.RE
.PP
.B NOTES
.PP
.RS 4
Strips only our fw_cfg segment from args (preserving other args). Removes hookscript if it matches ours. Leaves /var/lib/lamboot/<VMID>.json for forensic use (rm manually if desired).
